Package com.tapjoy

Interface Summary
TapjoyAwardPointsNotifier Any class calling awardTapPoints should implement TapjoyAwardPointsNotifier so it can receive the callback containing the virtual currency name/total info.
TapjoyEarnedPointsNotifier Notifier to inform the app whenever virtual currency has been earned.
TapjoyFeaturedAppNotifier Notifier class which sends callbacks whenever receiving Full Screen Ad data/response.
TapjoyNotifier Any class calling getTapPoints should implement TapjoyNotifier so it can receive the callback containing the virtual currency name/total info.
TapjoySpendPointsNotifier Any class calling spendTapPoints should implement TapjoySpendPointsNotifier so it can receive the callback containing the virtual currency name/total info.
TapjoyVideoNotifier  
 

Class Summary
TapjoyConnect Created by Tapjoy.
TapjoyConnectFlag Flags used in TapjoyConnect.requestTapjoyConnect(android.content.Context, java.lang.String, java.lang.String) to define special startup options.

These flags can also be defined in the meta-data tags in AndroidManifest.xml.
TapjoyDisplayAdSize Supported banner ad sizes for Banner Ads.
TapjoyFeaturedAppObject The TapjoyFeaturedAppObject represents a full screen ad object and is initialized when the server responds to the URL request for getting the feature app data is completed.
TapjoyLog This class is used to control debug messages to the console for Tapjoy SDK related classes.
TapjoyReEngagementAdStatus Status codes used in the callbacks for TapjoyReEngagementAdNotifier::getReEngagementAdResponseFailed.
TapjoyVideoStatus Status codes used in the callbacks for loadGameState and saveGameState.
